data.description: Welcome to this all brick home with fantastic bones, ready for your personal upgrades. The home features a formal dining room and breakfast area. Original hardwood runs throughout most of the home with a large laundry room, 2 car garage with an attached storage room. Located 10 minutes from RAFB! Offering $4000 cosmetic allowance with full price offer. If you are looking for a larger back yard, there is an adjacent lot also available for purchase!
